briefdescription.para: Returns active Camera instance (note: player's camera is not Camera instance - thus it return null)

briefdescription.para: Interpolation between camera instances (current camera becomes targetCamera at the end of interpolation)

parameterdescription.para: to which camera we want to interpolate
0 = without dynamics 1 = first half - acceleration, second half deceleration 2 = first third - acceleration, second third - linear movement, last third - deceleration
